Title: Quantum Limits in Interferometric GW Antennas in the Presence of Even
  and Odd coherent states
Authors: Nadeem A. Ansari, L. Di Fiore, M. A. Man'ko, V.I. Man'ko, S. Solimeno
  and F. Zaccaria
Comments: LATEX,14 pages,INFN-NA-IV-93/20, DSF-T-93/35
\\
  We discuss a model for interferometric GW antennas without dissipative or
active elements.
  It is predicted that the even and odd coherent states may play an alternative
role to squeezed vacuum states in reducing the optimal power of the input
laser.
